description: Haute Sausage is Chicago's Afro-Midwestern mobile sausage wagon; Upscale Hotdogs and home made potato chipsThick • Meaty • JuicyOwner Richard Levy was originally born in South Africa, and grew up eating Boerewors, a concoction all but unknown here in the states. Hoping to remedy this, Levy brought his own take on the classic meat fusion to the Chicago streets. Just what is Boerewors? Read on at Roaming Hunger's blog to find out: http://roaminghunger.com/blog/8277/its-getting-haute-in-here
name: Haute Sausage
